node.text: Ok People, it's showtime! :D From now i'll post regularly (one every months or more i hope!) a 20 minutes video mixshow with scratches, tone plays, juggles, remixes, ecc. This is the #1 and is an open format mixshow; the next will be dedicated to specific musical genres (Hip Hop, House, Dancehall, Funk, ecc.) or specific themes (80's, 90's, ecc). Are you ready to spend the next 20 minutes with DJ Delta? Let me know what you think!
